  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\"><img alt=\"House Whent.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/50px-House_Whent.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/75px-House_Whent.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/100px-House_Whent.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Sarya Whent</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sarya Whent by Helaenarts.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/350px-Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg\" width=\"350\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/525px-Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f4/Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/700px-Sarya_Whent_by_Helaenarts.jpeg 2x\" /></a><div>Sarya Whent, by Helaenarts ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crossing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crossing\">Crossing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_269_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">269</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sarya Whent</b> was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a>, and the fifth wife of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>. She is deceased, with no progeny.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Her relationship to other members of House Whent is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarya_Whent&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued3)#Sarya_Whent\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued3)\">Sarya Whent</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404140922\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.255 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 449/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10491/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8210/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1101/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 798/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.69 MB/50 MB\nLu